Package com.wjduquette.joe

Class TypeProxy<V>

java.lang.Object
com.wjduquette.joe.TypeProxy<V>
Type Parameters:
V - The native value type
All Implemented Interfaces:
JoeCallable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BooleanProxy, ErrorProxy, KeywordProxy, ListProxy, NumberProxy, PairProxy, StringProxy
public class TypeProxy<V> extends Object implements JoeCallable
A proxy for a native Java type. The proxy implements all required metadata and services for the type.
